title: The NBA Shake-Up?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth, and Spencer Hall discuss if the Nets’ performance last night means they need to make a move, if Russell Westbrook needs to be traded, and what are the chances that Eric Musselman is the right amount of excited after Arkansas beat #1 Auburn? All that and more!
